data.description: Waterfront condo with boat slip in Treasure Island, Fl!  This spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom Isle of Carpi unit has spectacular westerly views of the intercoastal waterway.  Only minutes from the Gulf of Mexico this beautiful unit has an updated kitchen with granite countertops, wood and tile floors throughout and new master bathroom.  The neighborhood of Isle of Capri is a mix of single family homes and condos.  Tennis, Pickleball, Basketball courts and a playground are located across the street at Roselli Park.  With only 4 units in the complex there are ample covered common areas for cooking out as well as a large private storage room.  30-day minimum rentals.  Boat slips owned by the association are first come first serve.  Perfectly located to enjoy everything the Suncoast and downtown St. Petersburg has to offer!
